d630d8b6-2f80-4a70-9522-046d3bfb9741	95268efd-4cf6-4f01-8735-5df131a52a6f	Using Qwen for Common Tasks	Qwen can assist with various tasks such as answering frequently asked questions, conducting initial bug reports, and gathering information about projects. This session will demonstrate how to use these features effectively.	1
