rom CSV file\\ndata = pd.read_csv('data.csv', engine=db)\\n# Extract columns we need for analysis\\ncols_to_load = ['column1', 'column2']\\n# Transform the data\\ndata_transformed = data[cols_to_load].mean()\\n# Save the transformed data to a new table\\noutput_table = sa.Table('output_table', sa.MetaData(), autoload_with=db)\\ndata_transformed.to_sql(output_table, con=db, index=False)"}]}	3
0fcb3a9f-7e99-463d-acc5-c8827fab84e4	20ee1463-4edf-4d58-8fca-e0aa9ab1cf6f	Understanding Financial Data Types	{"title":"Understanding Financial Data Types","sections":[{"type":"text","heading":"Introduction","text":"Financial data is the backbone of any financial analysis. It provides the necessary information for decision-making and forecasting."},{"type":"code","language":"Python","code":"# Example Python Code\\nimport pandas as pd\\n\\ndf = pd.read_csv('financial_data.csv')\\nprint(df.head())\\n"},{"type":"text","heading":"Types of Financial Data","text":"There are primarily four types of financial data: \\n1. Categorical Data - Represents categories or groups.\\n2. Numerical Data - Represents quantities and can be either discrete or continuous.\\n3. Time Series Data - Data recorded over a series of time periods.\\n4. Spatial Data - Data that includes geographical information."},{"type":"callout","variant":"note","text":"Why Understanding Data Types Matters"},{"type":"text","heading":"Importance in Financial Analysis","text":"Understanding data types is crucial for selecting appropriate analytical methods. For instance, time series analysis requires specific techniques compared to categorical analysis."},{"type":"quiz","question":"Which of the following is a type of financial data?","options":["Categorical Data","Numerical Data","Time Series Data","Spatial Data","All of the above"],"answer":"All of the above"},{"type":"text","heading":"Sources of Financial Data","text":"Financial data can come from various sources including:\\n1. Company Financial Statements\\n2. Market Research Reports\\n3. Government Publications\\n4. Online Databases and APIs"}]}	0
